<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She is now getting back to work as the modeling world resumes, with new restrictions, amid the coronavirus pandemic. </p>

<p>And Bella Hadid is making sure her skin is plump and glowing as she used a coffee scrub before heading to work on Thursday. </p>

<p>The 23-year-old model filmed her bare torso covered in the coffee grounds scrub and posted it to her Instagram Story. </p>

<p>Scrub-a-dub: Bella Hadid is making sure her skin is plump and glowing as she used a coffee scrub before heading to work on Thursday </p>

<p>'My bestie made me a coffee scrub before work this morning,' she wrote alongside the nude snaps. 'Blessed.' </p>

<p>She went on to tag her friend Lauren Perez calling her `skin queen.' </p>

<p>Bella recorded a boomerang video of her bare stomach and under cleavage covered in the brown scrub. </p>

<p>Coffee scrubs are known to reduce inflammation, increase circulation, reduce puffiness and the appearance of cellulite among other benefits.  </p>

